title: The Third Prince of the Fallen Kingdom has Regressed
alternative_titles: The 3rd Prince of the Fallen Kingdom Returns
Rise of the Fallen Kingdom's Third Prince
summary: The Third Prince of the Fallen Kingdom has Regressed Manhwa 멸망한 왕국의 3왕자가 회귀했다, The 3rd Prince of the Fallen Kingdom Returns, Rise of the Fallen Kingdom’s Third Prince Description: Yuri, the unruly third prince of the fallen Briol Kingdom. After meeting his end while wandering in guilt, he ended up regressing to the spring of his 13th year, before the Empire’s invasion began! “Briols do not abandon honor, even in death.” One harrowing regret is enough. The kingdom shall be saved from ruin!
